snippet.textDisplay: With business closures and not much aid being provided, many families are in dire situations with their income being greatly reduced or even stopped. The health of boomers is not more important than the livelihood of millions of people throughout the US. The responsibility lies with the parents of young children, the immuno-suppressed, and the elderly. As a 25 year old in the US, my bills, rent, and obligations do not go away because 5-10k people have a slightly more potent flu. Stop the panic, stop the misinformation, let people live their lives.
